Judul: MYSTERY DEEPENS OVER SPEED OF UNIVERSE'S EXPANSION
Abstrak:
For much of this decade, the two most precise gauges of the Universe’s rate of
expansion have been in glaring disagreement. Now, a highly anticipated independent
technique that cosmologists hoped would solve the conundrum is instead adding to the
confusion
